         <p>Purchased from Henry Raup Wagner in 1919.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <userestrict id="aspace_4ad13fc0864d8af09e629258a7722ae4">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>The Henry Raup Wagner Collection of Louisiana Manuscripts is the physical property of the Beinecke Rare Book and Manuscript Library, Yale University. Literary rights, including copyright, belong to the authors or their legal heirs and assigns. For further information, consult the appropriate curator.</p>  
      </userestrict>
